tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE transactions (transaction_id INT,
              timestamp TIMESTAMP,
              amount DECIMAL,
              description TEXT);

CREATE TABLE user_details (user_id INT,
              user_name VARCHAR(255),
              email VARCHAR(255),
              address TEXT);

CREATE TABLE transaction_logs (log_id INT,
              transaction_id INT,
              timestamp TIMESTAMP,
              user_id INT,
              log_details TEXT);

CREATE TABLE regulatory_data (regulation_id INT,
              regulation_name VARCHAR(255),
              description TEXT,
              timestamp TIMESTAMP);

CREATE TABLE timestamps (
  timestamp_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp_value TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE transactions (
  transaction_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  transaction_amount DECIMAL,
  transaction_date TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE users (
  user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_name VARCHAR(50),
  user_email VARCHAR(100),
  user_registered_at TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE audit_logs (
  log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  timestamp_id UUID,
  user_id UUID,
  action VARCHAR(50),
  log_timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE compliance_status (
  compliance_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id UUID,
  status VARCHAR(20),
  last_checked_at TIMESTAMP
)
